 xx-large;\">不包括總督察級或以上警務人員及<br />\n警務處正副處長</span></span><br />\n<br />\n*如果太急就轉6月12日到7月27日 (不包括7月28日當日）<br />\n重點係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拋返個波去前線警察</span></span>道<br />\n令佢哋當日開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對使用暴力有所顧忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立調查委員會則改為追究以上人士責任<br />\n處理警隊權力失衡現象及<br />\n公開警察通例所有條文等</span></span><br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我唔係覺得啲打人警察冇問題<br />\n只係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真真正正解決問題</span></span><br />\n係要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">令失控嘅權力架構撥亂反正</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我畀你真係可以告倒部分前線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">權力架構問題依舊<br />\n日後嘅日子無論邊個上場<br />\n政府都只會變本加厲</span></span><br />\n就正如大家點解重提真普選<br />\n係要從根本入手解決系統制度問題<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個方法之下<br />\n我哋更可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">塞住所謂撐警人士/擔心前線同事警察嘅口</span></span><br />\n佢哋嘅所謂<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撐警活動<br />\n會忽然間變成冇意義</span></span><br />\n如果再繼續所謂撐警嘅人<br />\n就可以被<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">標籤為政權高官打手</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將政權高官同警察正式分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">對我來講<br />\n追究警察責任係重要<br />\n但救返義士，救返香港更加重要</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b8828874dfbb75687a985eb788ee1441f02f887","tid":1331338,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57934c7cb8071ce75eaaaa2e39d911b74d25c023","tid":1331338,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"想班警察之後罷工/按章工作？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇可能！</span></